config PANICOS_DEVICE_RG35XX_PRO
	bool "anbernic/rg35xx-pro (Allwinner H700, LPDDR4)"
	select PANICOS_SOC_ALLWINNER_H700
	help
	  Anbernic RG35XX Pro — LPDDR4 DRAM variant (most common retail
	  hardware). U-Boot uses anbernic_rg35xx_h700_lpddr4_defconfig
	  with DCDC3 = 1100 mV.

	  If your hardware is the less-common LPDDR3 variant, build the
	  "rg35xx-pro-lpddr3" target instead — the U-Boot DRAM init
	  parameters and DCDC3 voltage differ between the two and a
	  mismatch will cause boot failure or instability.

	  Kernel: Linux 7.0.1 mainline + ROCKNIX patches.
